                <expan><abbr>Idib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> Au<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Herculi <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Ingenui<lb break="no" n="3"/>us <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Quir</abbr><ex>ina</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Rufinianus <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>eptimiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>S</abbr><ex>iscianorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>quaest</abbr><ex>or</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ollegii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>entonariorum</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>et Ingenui<lb break="no" n="9"/>a Rufina <lb n="10"/>cum suis <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>onum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Auf der linken Nebenseite eine abgearbeitete männliche Figur mit einer Schale in der Rechten, auf der rechten Nebenseite eine männliche Figur mit einer Schüssel mit Speisen in der Rechten und Tuch in der Linken. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona.</p>
            </div>
